(firstQuint)Post-Marketing Surveillance of Patients Using the Subretinal Retina Implant Alpha.

 This study is a non-invasive registry to monitor the safety and efficacy of patients using the CE-certified RETINA IMPLANT Alpha.

 For Germany, it is under the exceptions mentioned in 23b MPG (Medizinproduktegesetz).

 Its purpose is to collect data that is created during the regular therapy with the implant.

 No additional examinations are performed, except a patient questionnaire.

